<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Peter Hearn Electrical Ltd - NICEIC Registered Electrician in Fleetwood | 24/7 Emergency Service</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Need an electrician in Fleetwood? Peter Hearn Electrical offers professional electrical services. NICEIC registered. Call 07712 880441 for same-day service.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        :root {
            --primary: #0066FF;
            --secondary: #FFD700;
            --accent: #FF6B00;
            --dark: #0a1628;
            --light: #f8f9fa;
            --white: #ffffff;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        /* Header */
        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            padding: 0.75rem 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        header .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        @media (min-width: 769px) {
            header .container {
                padding: 0 2rem;
            }
        }
        
        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        
        .logo-img {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .powered-by {
            position: absolute;
            right: 2rem;
            top: -1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #999;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .powered-by:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .header-phone {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: var(--dark);
            padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .header-phone:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.4);
        }
        
        /* Hero with Video Background */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 7rem 2rem 5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066FF 0%, #FFD700 100%);
        }
        
        .hero-video {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 50%, rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 3;
            max-width: 900px;
        }
        
        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.95);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.6);
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        
        .hero-subtitle {
            text-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            opacity: 0.98;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 3rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .stat {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--secondary);
            text-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        
        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1.1rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: white;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            color: white;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        /* Services Section */
        .services {
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            background: var(--light);
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #666;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        .service-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        
        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.15);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .service-icon {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            border-radius: 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.25);
        }
        
        .service-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .service-card p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        /* Portfolio Section */
        .portfolio {
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            background: white;
        }
        
        .portfolio-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        
        .portfolio-item {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 4/3;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .portfolio-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .portfolio-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        
        /* CTA Section */
        .cta-section {
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .cta-section p {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: var(--dark);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem 2rem 2rem;
        }
        
        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .footer-section h3 {
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .footer-section p,
        .footer-section a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .footer-section a:hover {
            color: var(--secondary);
        }
        
        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .powered-footer {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }
        
        .powered-footer a {
            color: var(--secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .powered-footer a:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            .stat-number {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .cta-section h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .header-phone span {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <img src="logo.png" alt="Peter Hearn Electrical" class="logo-img">
                <div class="logo">Peter Hearn Electrical</div>
            </div>
            <a href="tel:07712880441" class="header-phone">
                <span>📞</span>
                <span>07712 880441</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline>
            <source src="hero-video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-badge">✅ NICEIC Registered Electrician</div>
            <h1>Professional Electrical Services in Fleetwood</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Fast, reliable electrical work from a trusted local electrician. Same-day emergency service available.</p>
            
            <div class="hero-stats">
                <div class="stat">
                    <span class="stat-number">15+</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Years Experience</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <span class="stat-number">24/7</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Emergency Service</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Satisfaction Guaranteed</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-buttons">
                <a href="tel:07712880441" class="btn btn-primary">
                    📞 Call Now: 07712 880441
                </a>
                <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">
                    Our Services
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section class="services" id="services">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Our Electrical Services</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Professional electrical work for homes and businesses across Fleetwood</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">⚡</div>
                    <h3>Emergency Repairs</h3>
                    <p>24/7 emergency electrical repairs. No power? Tripping fuse board? We're here to help, day or night.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">💡</div>
                    <h3>Installations</h3>
                    <p>Complete electrical installations including lighting, sockets, consumer units, and EV charging points.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">🔍</div>
                    <h3>Testing & Inspection</h3>
                    <p>NICEIC certified electrical testing, PAT testing, and safety inspections for landlords and homeowners.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">🏠</div>
                    <h3>Rewiring</h3>
                    <p>Full or partial house rewiring to bring your property up to current electrical safety standards.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">🔌</div>
                    <h3>Commercial Work</h3>
                    <p>Electrical services for shops, offices, and commercial properties across Fleetwood and surrounding areas.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">🛠️</div>
                    <h3>Fault Finding</h3>
                    <p>Expert electrical fault finding and diagnosis using professional testing equipment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Portfolio Section -->
    <section class="portfolio">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Recent Work</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Quality electrical work across Fleetwood and the Fylde Coast</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="portfolio-grid">
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="portfolio/work-1.jpg" alt="Electrical installation">
                </div>
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="portfolio/work-2.jpg" alt="Consumer unit upgrade">
                </div>
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="portfolio/work-3.jpg" alt="LED lighting installation">
                </div>
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="portfolio/work-4.jpg" alt="Commercial electrical work">
                </div>
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="portfolio/work-5.jpg" alt="Electrical testing">
                </div>
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <img src="portfolio/work-6.jpg" alt="Emergency repair">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Need an Electrician in Fleetwood?</h2>
            <p>NICEIC registered electrician. Same-day service available. Call now for a free quote.</p>
            <a href="tel:07712880441" class="btn btn-primary">
                📞 Call 07712 880441 Now
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Peter Hearn Electrical Ltd</h3>
                <p>NICEIC Registered Electrician</p>
                <p>9 Poulton Street</p>
                <p>Fleetwood, FY7 6LP</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Contact</h3>
                <a href="tel:07712880441">📞 07712 880441</a>
                <a href="http://www.phelec.co.uk" target="_blank">🌐 www.phelec.co.uk</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Service Areas</h3>
                <p>Fleetwood</p>
                <p>Cleveleys</p>
                <p>Thornton</p>
                <p>Poulton-le-Fylde</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>Hours</h3>
                <p>Mon-Fri: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
                <p>Sat: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
                <p>Sun: Emergency Only</p>
                <p><strong>24/7 Emergency Service</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Peter Hearn Electrical Ltd. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="powered-footer">
                <p>Demo website powered by <a href="https://aimindshift.consulting" target="_blank">AiMindShift</a> - AI-powered digital solutions for local businesses</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
